title: Bruno Passos 2nd Place Masters Run 2016 | Vans Pool Party | VANS
description:
Here’s how Bruno Passos, last year's winner, took 2nd place in the Masters division at the 2016 Vans Pool Party.

About Vans:
Vans®, a VF Corporation (NYSE: VFC) brand, is the original action sports footwear, apparel and accessories brand. Vans authentic collections are sold globally in more than 75 countries through a network of subsidiaries, distributors and international offices. Vans also owns and operates more than 450 retail locations around the world. The Vans brand promotes the action sports lifestyle, youth culture and creative self-expression through the support of athletes, musicians and artists and through progressive events and platforms such as the Vans Triple Crown of Surfing®, the Vans U.S. Open of Surfing, Vans Pool Party, Vans Custom Culture, Vans Warped Tour®, and Vans’ cultural hub and international music venue, the House of Vans.

transcripts: You can get that back tail in anytime, but right now we have last years winner and uh what can you say legend in the Brazilian skate world and the American skate world for that matter. Bruno Passos, what can you tell us about Bruno, yeah right here on our sheets it says he's from Vista, California. He may live there now but he's one of Brazil's finest, grew up in Rio de Janeiro, Brazil with Bob Burquest. Bob Burnquest usually credits Bruno Passos for why he's skateboarding and this guy Bruno's usually behind the camera filming Bob, really amazing skateboard filmmaker and still so good at skateboarding, 5 0 to fakie through the corner. 8 seconds to go right now and so far I think this is the best run we've seen in the masters final. It's definitely the craziest line rolling into the corner hitting the smith That is going to be time right there, that is a perfect run, I think that's going to be in the 80's for Bruno Passos. I wouldn't, I wouldn't put it past him, just fallen off, but that was well after time so the judges are not going to score him down on that. And Darren's just a fun guy to skate with, he's got a great attitude, he's geeky, and his love of skateboarding. [Music Playing].
